OL,4,CGovernment to ban single-use plastic
OL,5,Ccutlery
OL,6, The government has announced plans to
OL,7, ban single-use plastic cutlery, plates
OL,8, and polystyrene cups in England as part
OL,9, of what it calls a "war on plastic".
OL,11,FMinisters said the move would help to
OL,12,Freduce litter and cut the amount of
OL,13,Fplastic waste in oceans.
OL,15,FA consultation on the policy will
OL,16,Flaunch in the autumn - although the
OL,17,Fgovernment has not ruled out including
OL,18,Fother items in the ban.
OL,20,FBut environmental activists said more
OL,21,Furgent and wider action was needed.
